{"tid":2019112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"善用airdrop 功能","createTime":"2020-05-16T05:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T05:57:04.000Z","uid":166755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f4dcc22f7f154a7d6e641f95d2c24d1779d2c7","tid":2019112,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"相信唔少人都有用緊apple 記唔記得運動頭幾個月既airdrop 熱潮 出親街都一定會收到文宣 但呢家好似已經無咗呢回事 <br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">善用airdrop功能</span> 繼續比更加多人睇到香港既黑暗 eg琴日5月15號發生既事<br />\n<br />\n唔理你搭咩車 唔理你食咩餐廳 得閒手痕就share文宣 可能有啲人覺得出去貼連儂牆好危險 唔緊要 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Airdrop絕對係一個低成本高效益既行為</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n相信琴日既事大家都好失望 但唔好絕望 每人做多少少野 一定會有更多既改變 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足，煲底見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKc7zbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKc7zbY.jpg&h=4e952119&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUUawYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUUawYD.jpg&h=5713bd80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsX7zbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsX7zbZ.jpg&h=e78828f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Csdnn5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsdnn5B.jpg&h=869ee83f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iy7fH5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiy7fH5C.jpg&h=dc5d36ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eef1942dd72922752b82acf138485853f446cde","tid":2019112,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"3d547180e61a1ad3c3020eda6ab2cce75d17eceb","tid":2019112,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit