ttps://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=e541ca20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=b8325269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=88faa822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下"},{"pid":"ce433b97183b149283600ca3be550c6c18956937","tid":2019112,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4556df0985e4c03a9feff072ad5ab3af9b07f77","tid":2019112,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4cbc5a9ce9ff2998ac4fe5d1a7978e48c326af7","tid":2019112,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}